    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Spend Time With Children</strong>&mdash;The average father wastes many golden opportunities to attract and bind his children to him. Upon returning home from his business, he should find it a pleasant change to spend some time with his children.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 12-6-1877\" data-link=\"820.776\">The Signs of the Times, December 6, 1877</span>.</span></a></sup>",
