    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Associate With Them in Work and Sports</strong>&mdash;Fathers, ... combine affection with authority, kindness and sympathy with firm restraint. Give some of your leisure hours to your children; become acquainted with them; associate with them in their work and in their sports, and win their confidence. Cultivate friendship with them, especially with your sons. In this way you will be a strong influence for good.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">9<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 391.1\" data-link=\"135.1977\">The Ministry of Healing, 391, 392</span>.</span></a></sup>",
